{"tid":657559,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北京車展陪客狂聊8小時 交訂金前反悔！Sales氣到吐血倒地","createTime":"2018-05-08T08:24:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-08T10:35:13.000Z","uid":153228,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"787c69b924c581dead5a192540d3c28f27fe93f2","tid":657559,"uid":153228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T08:24:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ebc.net.tw/news.php?nid=111780\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ebc.net.tw%2Fnews.php%3Fnid%3D111780&d=y5mgkFxAUX7G1rq2ZOxvRjACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=4ea78198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ebc.net.tw/news.php?nid=111780</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d17ixjpazu3j94.cloudfront.net/images/2018/05/07/15256960723943d9AttnWQss.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd17ixjpazu3j94.cloudfront.net%2Fimages%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F15256960723943d9AttnWQss.jpg&h=8f194425&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲（圖/翻攝自騰訊視頻）<br />\n<br />\n第15屆北京國際汽車展覽剛圓滿落幕，卻有網友爆料，一名汽車銷售業務竟被客戶「氣到吐血」！北京車展共計吸引82萬人次參觀，不少大陸民眾趁著假期到車展逛逛，汽車銷售業務也使出渾身解數，希望能創下佳績，但卻傳出一名業務陪著客戶聊了一整天，但在交訂金的關鍵時刻，客戶卻突然反悔，讓業務難以接受，竟突發心肌梗塞，嘴角滲血送醫。<br />\n<br />\n一名網友在微博爆料，一名奧客在車展看上一款車，業務也熱心幫忙介紹，過程中一切都很正常，但諮詢的時間卻相當長，從車展開始一直談到下午，耗費約8個小時，期間業務耐心向客戶說明，客戶後來也表示要買車，連合約都簽好了，沒想到在交訂金的節骨眼上，客戶卻突然反悔，表示要回家和家人商量一下。<br />\n<br />\n▼（圖/翻攝自騰訊視頻）<br />\n<img src=\"https://ebcnews.s3.amazonaws.com/images/2018/05/07/15256961732881oP5W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Febcnews.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fimages%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F15256961732881oP5W.jpg&h=86625fc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n車展只有短短3天，而這位業務卻花費了一整天的時間，陪這一名客戶諮詢，沒想到最後卻無法成交，一聽到「回家商量」後，他難以接受彷彿晴天霹靂，竟突發心肌梗塞應聲倒地，嘴角還滲出血，最後被救護車載往醫院。消息傳出後，不少網友感嘆，「是用生命在做銷售！」、「心碎了，銷售不易啊！」<br />\n<br />\n▼業務被救護車載往醫院（圖/翻攝自微博）<img src=\"https://ebcnews.s3.amazonaws.com/images/2018/05/07/15256961977466v4RE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Febcnews.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fimages%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F15256961977466v4RE.jpg&h=8f50a537&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n還有人責備那名奧客，「不喜歡請不要傷害，更不要耍人家玩」、「沒有真心想買，問一下就該走人，從早談到下午，浪費人家時間沒辦法接其他客人，拖累人家一天沒收入，這不是砸人家飯碗嗎？」此外，也有業務出妙招，「車展上要直接問客戶今天能不能交錢，猶豫的就下一個，畢竟時間有限」。"},{"pid":"c05df9f282dd839d34e243fb5d8e8bd7a9e93e29","tid":657559,"uid":44171,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T08:26:21.000Z","msg":"又講支那人好有錢? 幾百萬既車都好似買菜咁? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ba6e39257738694f8d066555c4ae41f50c734ef","tid":657559,"uid":137694,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"c05df9f282dd839d34e243fb5d8e8bd7a9e93e29","tid":657559,"uid":44171,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T08:26:21.000Z","msg":"又講支那人好有錢? 幾百萬既車都好似買菜咁? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T08:27:56.000Z","msg":"關有冇錢咩事？"},{"pid":"5d678aaa180b1f240d3c8a24a9cda7a0c771b756","tid":657559,"uid":81183,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T08:28:29.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> sales狗下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 尊嚴都冇埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n慘過隊穿牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"434877ab7ebfd7389c259c14d0eebfa51b8ea40c","tid":657559,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T08:28:50.000Z","msg":"買Ford車會比人話25仔，梗係唔買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4c75920f1e18c21a8fa17196eb3a442925203bb","tid":657559,"uid":33789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T08:30:29.000Z","msg":"隊王隊穿牆?"},{"pid":"7b26ac190a3aef1fb7f414ec170626151c323e1b","tid":657559,"uid":44171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9ba6e39257738694f8d066555c4ae41f50c734ef","tid":657559,"uid":137694,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"c05df